
-- Required Files --

jquery.textchildren.js:
    Download the latest version from
    http://plugins.learningjquery.com/textchildren/
    and place in the annotation_text module directory.
    
jquery.wrapSelection.js:
    Download the latest version from
    http://plugins.jquery.com/project/wrapSelection
    and place in the annotation_text module directory.

-- Installation --

    For annotations to show up, you must enable the Annotation filter, and set it to run before any other filter.
